    "name": "GamerAworlD",
    "steam_appid": 2356520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/4f7ed490bc670d86e8db3a1f3d41698b.avif?t=1770807749\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《GamerAworlD》是一款轻松惬意的桌面游戏。在游戏中，你将置身于漂浮在云上的小小空岛。你既可以一边建设自己的空岛一边享受安静平和的独处时光；也可以偶尔和其他空岛的玩家发送纸飞机互诉衷肠；还可以骑着你的小摩托，走出你的空岛，和NPC一起探索丰富多彩的游戏世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新春套装，新上线！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/b086b62a25aa1ce426bffc12b30f3d8c.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/31943a1f84ce146fffd47d5717c2c9dc.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/2854091aa9e37d23421011094a198a94.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种挂机模式与效率小工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >默认模式：游戏会以设置里的分辨率以及全屏选项开始挂机，也就是我们默认的挂机模式，简单直接！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/093c28cf75e9a524245fbbd969ab3643.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >壁纸模式：从游戏一开始就有的挂机模式，游戏在桌面壁纸层运行，让你的桌面更有趣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/43ac9c506c2f5c44df59d6d7b4ae69c5.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌宠模式：这个版本新推出的模式！在玩家岛屿上，玩家的小屋就是桌面模式显示的区域，而在NPC的岛屿上，会显示我们精心设计的小场景～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/38dd3dd6a4e018dca239416cd03f5e66.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，我们在各个模式下都提供了如下效率小工具：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >番茄时钟</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >便签/日记本</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Todo List</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >习惯追踪</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >里程碑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间线</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分享</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挂机奖励和商店</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入挂机模式游戏会自动运行并爆金币，爆出的金币可以在NPC处兑换家具和衣服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/e7665ca372a39f2aaee2b48e7d7fe90c.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在自己空岛的镜子处可以换上刚买的新衣服～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/c6a17d2ffe3b46821364e7f1b036d6e2.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在的Demo里已经包含了80多种家具以及20多种服饰，完整版里会有更多。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装修系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/b5ce113a3ffcc43348c8300711c5dfef.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过游戏中的装修系统来布置自己的小岛，让你的小岛与众不同。在各式各样的家具中，我们埋藏了很多的游戏彩蛋，等着你去发现。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纸飞机系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/3393b65bcaa02900c5f46b767eafa153.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/107aee1218a7a3fbb4f887d1adc57853.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，纸飞机是和弹幕在视频网站类似的存在。我们希望在这个游戏里陪伴玩家的除了美丽的风景，轻松的音乐以及可爱的NPC，还有来自陌生玩家善意的祝福。如果位陌生玩家的祝福让你感到温暖或者被治愈，别忘了回赠一个礼物，纸飞机的作者也会被你的善意所治愈。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NPC和他们的岛屿</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，会有NPC来到你的岛屿陪你一起工作学习，当然，你也可以前往他们的岛屿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/bce3e4e2aadad3473ce81bc087fb0ae9.poster.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/bce3e4e2aadad3473ce81bc087fb0ae9.webm?t=1770807749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/b0c68cd7fb1ffc513f81a4bbb5e3f7e6.poster.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/b0c68cd7fb1ffc513f81a4bbb5e3f7e6.webm?t=1770807749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/dbaeb040356631c1e22f717ce4e61055.poster.avif?t=1770807749\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/dbaeb040356631c1e22f717ce4e61055.webm?t=1770807749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356520/extras/dbaeb040356631c1e22f717ce4e61055.mp4?t=1770807749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来计划</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多的NPC岛屿和剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家联系系统</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demo还有很多Bug和体验问题，希望你多多包容，有什么问题和建议可以加玩家群反馈给我，提前谢过啦。好啦，我现在要回去加班加点继续工作了，之后我们会持续更新，带来更多的内容！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ玩家群：823429026</strong></p>",
